{"tid":1049352,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來而家賣Rainbow吸塵機要做床單","createTime":"2019-03-06T08:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T04:18:44.000Z","uid":240813,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6c001ebca045b60dfc667917be1b29decebe791c","tid":1049352,"uid":240813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n前幾日約咗個Rainbow人妻sale屎上黎做demo<br />\n好似叫Valxxxx<br />\n風韻猶存型<br />\n著住件鬆身Tee<br />\n開頭喺廳度示範都正正常常<br />\n都係間中烏低吓借D二俾我𥄫吓咁<br />\n部機差唔多要三萬蚊<br />\n佢地做到一張單有幾千蚊佣<br />\n佢見我唔想買咁<br />\n就突然話不如入房做demo<br />\n我話一男一女入房唔係咁好<br />\n佢就哄過黎話唔緊要啦，大家成年人怕咩<br />\n咁我咪帶佢入房睇吓佢想點"},{"pid":"b9f4f2bfb118ed53135b52f31a391505b872bac9","tid":1049352,"uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76710e36745fe2cc5eafc6ed202f54828f283788","tid":1049352,"uid":19397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"加速加甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a46463980d051218f4f8717edee189f95a01f8","tid":1049352,"uid":7015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"Lm睇Rainbow吸床單"},{"pid":"aeded7e8c8f2671045c7bc81cc8a16acd71a2d67","tid":1049352,"uid":41334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"屋企買咗 用咗兩年 幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79030082546b36ea59480f4ea805ea0e9645ce3c","tid":1049352,"uid":240813,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"佢入到去就烏低身問我可唔可以插<br />\n我打咗個突<br />\n原來係插電制<br />\n都唔知係咪暗示D咩<br />\n插完之後佢突然就話好high<br />\n問我可唔可以上床<br />\n咁我作為一個男人<br />\n本能反應拒絕唔到<br />\n就答佢好啦<br />\n我正諗住拉起件衫嘅時候<br />\n佢好似發現我誤會咗咁<br />\n話個冷氣機太高<br />\n要踩上張床度<br />\n真係好老尷"},{"pid":"ce3a9336cb8